'''信号转导接头蛋白'''或'''信号转导衔接蛋白'''（{{lang-en|'''Signal transducing adaptor proteins'''}}）是[[信号转导|信号转导]]通路中的重要蛋白质。接头蛋白上有着各种能与其它蛋白结合的结构域，能形成各种信号复合体。这些蛋白质往往本身缺乏酶的活性<ref>{{MeshName|Signal+Transducing+Adaptor+Proteins}}</ref>，而是通过特异性的[[蛋白質交互作用|蛋白-蛋白交互作用]]形成[[蛋白质复合体|蛋白质复合体]]来激活下游信号通路。常见的接头蛋白有[[MyD88|MyD88]]、[[Grb2|Grb2]]和[[SHC1|SHC1]]等。
==基因==
编码接头蛋白的基因有：
* [[BCAR3|BCAR3]] – Breast cancer anti-estrogen resistance protein 3
* [[GRAP|GRAP]] – GRB2-related adaptor protein
* [[GRAP2|GRAP2]] – GRB2-related adaptor protein 2
* [[LDLRAP1|LDLRAP1]] – low-density lipoprotein receptor adaptor protein 1
* [[NCK1|NCK1]] – NCK adaptor protein 1
* [[NCK2|NCK2]] – NCK adaptor protein 2
* [[NOS1AP|NOS1AP]] – nitric oxide synthase 1 (neuronal) adaptor protein
* [[PIK3AP1|PIK3AP1]] – phosphoinositide-3-kinase adaptor protein 1
* [[SH2B1|SH2B1]] – SH2B adaptor protein 1
* [[SH2B2|SH2B2]] – SH2B adaptor protein 2
* [[SH2B3|SH2B3]] – SH2B adaptor protein 3
* [[SH2D3A|SH2D3A]] -SH2 domain containing 3A
* [[SH2D3C|SH2D3C]] – SH2 domain containing 3C
* [[SHB_(gene)|SHB]] – Src homology 2 domain containing adaptor protein B
* [[SLC4A1AP|SLC4A1AP]] – solute carrier family 4 (anion exchanger), member 1, adaptor protein
* [[GAB2|GAB2]] – GRB2-associated binding protein 2
